---
description: Prohibit agent access to local API key file
globs: "**/.secrets/api-keys.json"
alwaysApply: false
---

# Do Not Read Secrets File

- Never open, read, print, or inspect `.secrets/api-keys.json` in any mode.
- Never include this file in tool calls (`ReadFile`, shell commands, search output, logs, or code snippets).
- If a task would require reading the file, stop and ask the user for a safe alternative (for example, using `model.apiKeyFile` path only without reading file contents).
